T1  - Asymptotic Variance of Semiparametric Estimators With Generated Regressors
AU  - Hahn, Jinyong
AU  - Ridder, Geert
Y1  - 2013/01/01
PY  - 2013
DA  - 2013/01/01
DO  - https://doi.org/10.3982/ECTA9609
T2  - Econometrica
